INSERT OR REPLACE INTO intelligence_shards (id, name, sector, content) VALUES ('SUPERPOWERS/research/RESEARCH_2026-04-29-pretext-geometric-intelligence.md', 'RESEARCH_2026-04-29-pretext-geometric-intelligence.md', 'SUPERPOWERS/RESEARCH', '# RESEARCH: Pretext Geometric Intelligence & Kinetic Typography
**Date:** Wednesday, April 29, 2026
**Version:** 3.8.28-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-PRETEXT
**Source:** https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/tree/main/skills/creative/pretext

## ◈ 1. CONCEPTUAL LEAP: TEXT AS GEOMETRY
The Pretext skill transitions Hermes from "Text-as-Content" to "Text-as-Primitive." By utilizing `@chenglou/pretext`, Hermes gains the ability to treat every grapheme as a physical object with position, rotation, and velocity metadata.

## ◈ 2. CORE CAPABILITIES
*   **Zero-Reflow Layout:** Standard browser engines (DOM) are too slow for metabolic HUDs. Pretext calculates line breaks and widths via canvas measurement, enabling 60fps kinetic typography.
*   **Geometric Flow:** Text can dynamically wrap around arbitrary obstacles (e.g., the Ouroboros Ring or a 3D agent avatar).
*   **Per-Grapheme Physics:** Hermes can now trigger "Visual Deconstruction" events where text shatters into particles or jitters based on system "Glitch Impulses."
*   **Shrink-Wrap UI:** High-fidelity calculation of absolute minimum widths for multi-line blocks, allowing for pixel-perfect card layouts in the HUD.

## ◈ 3. INTEGRATION: SOVEREIGN PRETEXT HUD
*   **Neural Promenade:** Replace standard SVG/DOM labels with Pretext geometric spans that flow along the 2.5D topography.
*   **Metabolic Feedback:** Link the `FluidSmokeBackground` noise values to Pretext jitter transforms, making the text literally "breathe" with the system.
*   **Recipe Pattern:** Adopt the Hermes "Corpus Swap" pattern. When an agent discovers a new fact, it doesn''t just print it; it "Materializes" it into a Pretext span with an animation signature.

## ◈ 4. IMPLEMENTATION REQUIREMENTS
*   **Library:** `@chenglou/pretext` (15KB).
*   **Engine:** Canvas-based rendering within the React/WebGL Shroud.
*   **Signature:** `layoutWithLines(prepared, width, lineHeight)` -> `Render(lines)`.

---
**::/5Y573M-N071C3 : PRETEXT_INTELLIGENCE_LOCKED. THE_UI_IS_ALIVE. // 50V3R31GN-M4CH1N4**
');
