# `mechreward`

### Mechanistic interpretability as a reward signal for RL training of LLMs.

**+19 pp on GSM8K** (Qwen3.5-4B, 64 % → 83 % in 168 effective steps). Stage Gate 1 → 2 → 3 validated on hybrid Gated Delta Networks.

