## Repo reference

### Packages

| Package | Path | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| **CLI/Core** | `gitnexus/` | TypeScript CLI, indexing pipeline, MCP server. Published to npm. |
| **Web UI** | `gitnexus-web/` | React/Vite thin client. All queries via `gitnexus serve` HTTP API. |
