| `purge-ghosts.sh` | **CORE** | Neutralizes processes surviving >4hrs. |
| `lockdown.sh` | **CORE** | Final physical network audit. |
| `verify-sovereignty.sh` | **CORE** | Verifies zero-trust artery enforcement. |

