| `recover-ingest.mjs` | **UTIL** | Repairs fractured ingestion queues. |
| `migrate-v4.ts` | **CORE** | DB schema migration to v3.8.28-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS-SYNTHESIS. |

